OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784548078
OL,3,CUUP launching 'independent
OL,4,Cconfidential' review into Jeffrey
OL,5,CDonaldson
OL,7,FThe Ulster Unionists are to establish
OL,8,Fan "independent confidential process"
OL,9,Finto potential complaints during
OL,10,FJeffrey Donaldson's time in the party.
OL,12,FDonaldson, 63, was convicted at Newry
OL,13,FCrown Court last month of 18 sex
OL,14,Foffences, including one count of rape,
OL,15,Frelating to the abuse of two women
OL,16,Fwhen they were children.
OL,18,FThe offences were committed between
OL,19,F1985 and 2008.
OL,26,@pD@DOUpD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/9
