OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784548078
OL,3,CUUP launching 'independent
OL,4,Cconfidential' review into Jeffrey
OL,5,CDonaldson
OL,7,FThe two victims gave evidence against
OL,8,Fhim during the trial, during which
OL,9,FDonaldson had denied the offences.
OL,11,FHis wife Eleanor Donaldson, 60, was
OL,12,Ffound to have aided and abetted his
OL,13,Fcrimes following a trial of the facts,
OL,14,Fwhich was granted on mental health
OL,15,Fgrounds.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
