CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784548078
OL,3,CUUP launching 'independent
OL,4,Cconfidential' review into Jeffrey
OL,5,CDonaldson
OL,7,FOn Monday, Ulster Unionist Party (UUP)
OL,8,Fleader Jon Burrows confirmed it would
OL,9,Fappoint an independent external
OL,10,Forganisation to provide a confidential
OL,11,Froute for anyone who had information
OL,12,For concerns about Jeffrey Donaldson
OL,13,Fduring his time in the party.
OL,15,FDonaldson began his political career
OL,16,Fwith the UUP, joining in his late
OL,17,Fteens.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
