PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784548078
OL,3,CUUP launching 'independent
OL,4,Cconfidential' review into Jeffrey
OL,5,CDonaldson
OL,7,FIn the early 1980s, he worked as
OL,8,Fpersonal assistant for former
OL,9,FConservative cabinet minister and then
OL,10,FUUP MP Enoch Powell.
OL,12,FIn 1985, aged 22, he was elected to a
OL,13,Fshort-lived incarnation of the
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland Assembly and later
OL,15,Fbecame MP for Lagan Valley in 1997.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
