PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784548078
OL,3,CUUP launching 'independent
OL,4,Cconfidential' review into Jeffrey
OL,5,CDonaldson
OL,7,FFollowing a fractured relationship
OL,8,Fwith then UUP leader David Trimble
OL,9,Fover aspects of the Good Friday
OL,10,FAgreement, he quit the UUP in 2003 and
OL,11,Fdefected to the Democratic Unionist
OL,12,FParty, where he would eventually
OL,13,Fbecome leader.
OL,15,FOn Monday, the UUP said a "rapid
OL,16,Freview" after Donaldson's conviction
OL,17,Fdid not find any formal nor informal
OL,18,Fcomplaint nor concern, and the party
OL,19,Fsaid it had not been contacted by the
OL,20,FPSNI "at any point" about the matters
OL,21,Fconcerned.
OL,26,@wD@[OUxD@GO]|D@FOU|D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784548078
OL,3,CUUP launching 'independent
OL,4,Cconfidential' review into Jeffrey
OL,5,CDonaldson
OL,7,FHowever, the party said this was a
OL,8,F"first step" and "not the end of the
OL,9,Fmatter".
OL,11,FIt said the new independent review
OL,12,Fwill also examine the party's
OL,13,Fsafeguarding arrangements.
OL,15,FMr Burrows has also written to Chief
OL,16,FConstable Jon Boutcher to offer
OL,17,F"support for a proactive public
OL,18,Fappeal" about Donaldson.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@LO]pD@ROUqD@GO]yD@AOUzD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
