FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784548078
OL,3,CUUP launching 'independent
OL,4,Cconfidential' review into Jeffrey
OL,5,CDonaldson
OL,7,FThe UUP said it believes that only a
OL,8,Ffully independent inquiry can
OL,9,Festablish "what, if anything, was
OL,10,Fknown about Donaldson across his
OL,11,Fentire public career" by political
OL,12,Fparties, the police services, security
OL,13,Fagencies and Government.
OL,15,FIt said there are "important lessons"
OL,16,Fto be examined about vetting,
OL,17,Fsafeguarding and public appointments
OL,18,Fas it called in incoming prime
OL,19,Fminister Andy Burnham to establish
OL,20,Fsuch an inquiry.
OL,26,@qD@KOUsD@UO]wD@SOUwD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
