PN,41208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784548078
OL,3,CUUP launching 'independent
OL,4,Cconfidential' review into Jeffrey
OL,5,CDonaldson
OL,7,FThe DUP has also launched its own
OL,8,Findependent examination into
OL,9,FDonaldson's time within the party,
OL,10,Fwhile the Northern Ireland Assembly
OL,11,Fhas begun a review into any
OL,12,Fallegations of alleged abuse or
OL,13,Finappropriate behaviour associated
OL,14,Fwith his time in Stormont.
OL,16,FDonaldson is currently being held at
OL,17,FMaghaberry Prison in his former
OL,18,Fparliamentary constituency of Lagan
OL,19,FValley awaiting sentencing.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/9
