OL,3,CUUP launching 'independent
OL,4,Cconfidential' review into Jeffrey
OL,5,CDonaldson
OL,7,FLast week, his lawyer said he is to
OL,8,Flaunch an appeal.
OL,10,FEarlier this month, he was removed
OL,11,Ffrom the Privy Council after he asked
OL,12,Ffor his name to be taken off the list
OL,13,Fof members of the body of senior
OL,14,Fadvisers to the King.
